{"title":"Build a Hexo blog based on github-pages","date":"2018-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","slug":"hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages","tags":["Hexo"],"categories":["notes"],"updated":"2019-05-29T10:30:52.272Z","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\">Quick Start<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Quick-Start\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"Precondition\">Precondition<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Precondition\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li>git : deploy to github</li>\n<li>node.js : Hexo 基于 node.js开发的</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Environment\">Environment<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Environment\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li><p>git </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># version</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git --version</span><br><span class=\"line\">git version 2.17.2 (Apple Git-113)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>node.js</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># version</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">node -v</span><br><span class=\"line\">v7.2.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Install-Hexo\">Install Hexo<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Install-Hexo\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Init-Hexo-Folder\">Init Hexo Folder<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Init-Hexo-Folder\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir spaco</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> spaco</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\">Run server<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Run-server\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo server</span><br><span class=\"line\">Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000 . Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\">Create a new post<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Create-a-new-post\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server-1\">Run server<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Run-server-1\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo server</span><br><span class=\"line\">Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000 . Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Replace-theme\">Replace theme<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Replace-theme\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> spaco/themes</span><br><span class=\"line\">git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/elmorec/hexo-theme-inside.git inside</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> ../</span><br><span class=\"line\">vim _config.yml</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># replace default theme to inside</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">theme: landscape =&gt; theme: inside</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo server</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># theme has changed</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-GitHub\">Deploy to GitHub<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Deploy-to-GitHub\"></a></h3><p><code>need ssh-key already registered in GitHub</code></p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>Create repostory</p>\n<p>your_github_name.github.io</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Deployment config</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim _config.yml</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># like this</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">type</span>: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: git@github.com:spaco/spaco.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"Clean-static-files\">Clean static files<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Clean-static-files\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\">Generate static files<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Generate-static-files\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo generate </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># hexo g</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\">Deploy to remote sites<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Deploy-to-remote-sites\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo deploy</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># hexo d</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deployment</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Effective\">Effective<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Effective\"></a></h3><p>open <code>your-page.github.io</code> in the browser</p>\n<h3 id=\"Replace-domain-name\">Replace domain name<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#Replace-domain-name\"></a></h3><h3 id=\"References\">References<a href=\"post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages#References\"></a></h3><p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/863f3f2d1733\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">github+Hexo搭建blog</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://juejin.im/post/598eeaff5188257d592e55bb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">浅析 Hexo 搭建博客的原理</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Build kafka application with python","slug":"MQ-build-kafka-application-with-python"},"next":{"title":"Deploy Hexo blog based on travis-CI","slug":"hexo-deploy-hexo-blog-based-on-travis-CI"},"link":"https://spaco.github.io/post/hexo-blog-based-on-github-pages/","toc":[{"title":"Quick Start","id":"Quick-Start","index":"1","children":[{"title":"Precondition","id":"Precondition","index":"1.1"},{"title":"Environment","id":"Environment","index":"1.2"},{"title":"Install Hexo","id":"Install-Hexo","index":"1.3"},{"title":"Init Hexo Folder","id":"Init-Hexo-Folder","index":"1.4"},{"title":"Run server","id":"Run-server","index":"1.5"},{"title":"Create a new post","id":"Create-a-new-post","index":"1.6"},{"title":"Run server","id":"Run-server-1","index":"1.7"},{"title":"Replace theme","id":"Replace-theme","index":"1.8"},{"title":"Deploy to GitHub","id":"Deploy-to-GitHub","index":"1.9"},{"title":"Clean static files","id":"Clean-static-files","index":"1.10"},{"title":"Generate static files","id":"Generate-static-files","index":"1.11"},{"title":"Deploy to remote sites","id":"Deploy-to-remote-sites","index":"1.12"},{"title":"Effective","id":"Effective","index":"1.13"},{"title":"References","id":"References","index":"1.14"}]}]}